text: Laura Conz Dall'Ora (born 1 September 1962) is an Italian equestrian. She competed in two events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:Italian female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Italy Category:Equestrians at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Milan
